The paper discusses the use of neural networks for visual object classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper focuses on integrating visual knowledge with natural language, which is a topic in natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the challenges in crowd-sourcing data, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with video data, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
